data.description: What A Great Place To Call Home & In The Heart Of Buffalo! This rambler home has been renovated! Kitchen offers updated maple stained cabinets and lots of storage & counter space. Also a pantry, appliance & linen closet too. Oak floors have been refinished. Living room w/arch way and beautiful bay window. New 2 panel doors on the main. Main floor bedrooms with good size closets. Bathroom w/jetted tub, pedal sink, vinyl flooring. Cozy lower level family room w/chairrail detailing. Office/den (Could be converted into a bedroomby adding an egress window & closet) Updates 100 Amp, Roof 9 yrs old (30 year certainteed Landmark Shingles) Marvin windows, Exterior Cedar siding (painted 2023)  Exterior doors, CA, gutters. Sewer line to street has been replaced, new drain tile & pump, 6' Privacy fence and lilac hedge making a private backyard. 20x22 garage w/cement flrs, storage, insulated garage door.
